    EnterMarkets Geoff cZRX
    Assert Equal (Erc20 cZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 100e9)
    Assert Equal (CToken cZRX CollateralBalance Geoff) (Exactly 100e9)
    Assert Equal (Comptroller AssetsIn Geoff) [(Address cZRX)]

