Test "Transfer cToken successfully"
    CollateralCap
    CToken cZRX SetCollateralCap 20e9
    EnterMarkets Geoff cZRX
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX cZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 cZRX
    Assert Equal (Erc20 cZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e9)
